egível à luz do que era Portugal nos anos 60.\nChamando a atenção para a injustiça da repressão e das perseguições políticas, a peça – designada por &quot;apoteose trágica&quot; pelo Autor – esteve proibida até 1974 e foi pela primeira vez levada à cena apenas em 1978, no Teatro Nacional, numa encenação do próprio Sttau Monteiro.\n\nFonte: http://www.prof2000.pt/users/jsafonso/Port/luar.htm<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"4571818248215938171\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'9_book_6018056\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"0doP9ewNz/ZKaRSU/04H0wiy+qcRwPgPw57X1IWrUsPsmbdvcnUezYHQbFxICUE0NxGIAOKB8eaStYHmrM5d4Q==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"6018056\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"9_book_6018056\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/2605280-apari-o\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Want to Read<\/span>\n<span class=\'progressIndicator\'>saving…<\/span>\n<\/button>\n<\/form>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div c